Arrays Method : 
=================
1. Arrays.toString(arr)      : Returns the elements of the array as Strings.
2. Arrays.deepToString(arr)  : Returns the elements of the multi- dimensional array as Strings.
2. Arrays.sort(arr)          : Sorts the array.
3. Arrays.fill(arr, value)   : Fills 'value' in all the elements.

4. Arrays.copyOf(arr,length) : Returns an array of given length which is a copy of the given array.
  Eg. Chapter3